      <scopecontent id="aspace_3137dda17506ad994e22e7f80f18f849">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Clutterbuck's work was published as: The history and antiquities of the county of Hertford, compiled from the best printed authorities and original records, by Robert Clutterbuck (London: Nichols, Son, and Bentley, 1815-1827).</p>  
